    Black Aracnia recives Brightblades communication and finally gets a real 
feel of accomplishment. She looks to the monitor to see Brightblades 
signiture by the Maximal cruiser.
    "Ah, Brightblade! If you dont know already, Im the current Predacon 
Commander until MEgatron takes command. Im going to download the information 
now." She says, very kindly, unlike her true nature.
    Paralysis begins the download while Aracnia turns to Thunder Hammer. She 
looks him over, "Ah, for now you can take a break. Take the time to go into 
your beast mode and hunt, or something. Scout around and see if you cant talk 
to Megatron for me."
